ZH: 我始终相信你。
EN: I always trust you.

ZH: 他发给我一个简短的信息。
EN: He sent me a brief message.

ZH: 我信任他的判断。
EN: I trust his judgment.

ZH: 她对我保持守信用。
EN: She keeps her word to me.

ZH: 我信心十足地去追求我的梦想。
EN: I pursue my dreams with full confidence.

ZH: 信念让人变得更加坚强。
EN: Belief makes people stronger.

ZH: 他们是你忠实的信徒。
EN: They are your faithful followers.

ZH: 我对未来充满信心。
EN: I am full of confidence in the future.

ZH: 她代表了公司的信誉。
EN: She represents the company's reputation.

ZH: 请相信我，我会尽全力帮助您。
EN: Please trust me, I will do my best to help you.

ZH: 这只是一个误传，别太信谣言。
EN: It's just a misunderstanding, don't believe rumors too easily.

ZH: 他总是给我带来好消息。
EN: He always brings me good news.

ZH: 我们希望你对我们的团队抱有信任。
EN: We hope you have trust in our team.

ZH: 信守承诺非常重要。
EN: Keeping promises is very important.

ZH: 他用言行赢得了我的信赖。
EN: He won my trust with his words and actions.

ZH: 我们必须信守约定。
EN: We must keep our promises.

ZH: 他认为信的力量可以改变一切。
EN: He believes the power of faith can change everything.

ZH: 我们盼望着得到您的信任。
EN: We look forward to earning your trust.

ZH: 希望你可以放心，我们会处理好这件事情。
EN: Hope you can trust us, we will handle this matter well.

ZH: 他用行动证明了他的价值和信念。
EN: He proved his worth and belief through actions.
